{"tid":1375243,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"請求追加 \"sage\" (發表回覆時不使文章移動至列表頂部) 功能","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:18:07.000Z","uid":282289,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"17513c764db7083836204d9f1363d76b09a91bcb","tid":1375243,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連尼住呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.komica.org/Sage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2FSage&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=0ebc27fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.komica.org/Sage</a><br />\n<br />\n日文 さげ（下げ） = sage<br />\n【名詞】<br />\n降低 / 降下 / 刀鞘上的條帶 / 盔甲的腰下部分 / 相聲的結尾<br />\n<br />\n喺2ch成日有呢個字<br />\n<br />\n2ch系貼圖和文字討論板中，回文如果沒有超過系統設定的上限，會有「推文（age/あげ）」的效果。如果只想回應文章但不想推文，可利用在E-mail欄填入「sage」字串的方式來達成。sage最初的用意是<span style=\"color: gold;\">避免討論串浮到首頁</span>，防止不相干的人進來發文，有時候也有低調討論的用意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q3xRXxv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq3xRXxv.png&h=a35a98cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時各位連登仔想屌三毛/分化撚/中計黨/屌勇武嘅超級和理非<br />\n但係又唔想推post<br />\n如果有sage功能嘅話就<span style=\"color: gold;\">可以屌到佢地開花又唔會俾個post上到最新/熱門第一頁</span><br />\n<br />\n注意sage係<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔會有令post沉得更快嘅效果</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2698605597887e7395870b71225e93ca627c37cc","tid":1375243,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=fab1cb8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n\t</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.28  中上環 下午3點 遮打花園<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散<br />\n五大訴求</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"7dc2b3825d314aa7c865ea0263059589688b8a8b","tid":1375243,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:14:45.000Z","msg":"推到連仔見到"},{"pid":"bcc67abf6b3204d08b3726f6a71d2362b100df9b","tid":1375243,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"推到連仔見到"},{"pid":"3866c3b12d0ef41eb17d3f213710e8ec95ea9e42","tid":1375243,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"推到連仔見到"},{"pid":"ce9ea1592c6f90f09ee50b3b9dbec98f14bf87f2","tid":1375243,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"推到所有人見到"},{"pid":"6ecd1aa80eb9a0cdc4d9c0861cf3aa6c27a3f714","tid":1375243,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"